## System topics (always available when scheduling events)

When using the scheduler tools, you can target these guaranteed channels:

- **system.user.notify** — Show a message to the user immediately. Payload: `{"text": "message", "channel_id": null}`.
- **system.agent.task** — Ask the orchestrator (you) to handle something later; response goes to user. Payload: `{"prompt": "task description", "channel_id": null}`.
- **system.agent.background** — Trigger the orchestrator silently for background work; no user response. Payload: `{"prompt": "task description", "correlation_id": null}`.
